short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Recycles tabs left behind by tools like Zoom and Figma when they open their native app.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When web apps like Zoom and Figma open their native application, they leave behind a tab. 

This extension closes those extra tabs!


Currently Supported Apps:
Figma - http://figma.com
Zoom - http://zoom.us
